column12: GENE THERAPY FOR PITUITARY ADENOMA AND OTHER ENDOCRINE DISORDERS
column13: Virus vectors containing selected genes encoding proteins capable of modulating pituitary tumor or gland physiology and methods for using these vectors in the treatment of pituitary adenomas, pituitary hyperfunction and hypofunction, dysfunction of the hypothallamic/pituitary axis, and neuroendocrine diseases mediated by the pituitary gland are provided.
